  <name>AnaFis</name>
  <summary>Advanced Numerical Analysis and Fitting Interface System</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      AnaFis is a powerful desktop application for scientific data analysis and numerical computing.
      It combines the performance of Rust with modern web technologies to provide a comprehensive
      suite of tools for scientists, engineers, and researchers.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Advanced spreadsheet with formula evaluation and unit support</li>
      <li>Uncertainty propagation with symbolic mathematics (Python/SymPy)</li>
      <li>Unit conversion with dimensional analysis</li>
      <li>Curve fitting algorithms with visualization</li>
      <li>Monte Carlo simulations for statistical analysis</li>
      <li>Detachable tabs for multi-monitor workflows</li>
      <li>LaTeX rendering for mathematical expressions</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
